<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How does the free trial work?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Every plan starts with a 14-day free trial. Contact our team and your account will be set up within 24 hours — you'll receive login details by email. No payment details needed to get started."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What counts as a campus building?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Any physical building you manage keys and doors for — dorms, academic buildings, rec centres, etc. Each one counts as one campus building in your plan."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, at any time. Contact us and we'll handle the change. Upgrades take effect immediately; downgrades apply at the end of your billing period."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Where is my data stored?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Your data is stored on our managed infrastructure in isolated, private databases. Enterprise customers get a fully dedicated environment — no shared resources. Your data never mingles with other tenants'."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is there a per-key or per-door limit?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "No hard limits. Track as many keys and doors as your campus needs."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How does cancellation work?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Cancel any time by contacting us. Your data export is available for 30 days after cancellation."
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>
</head>
<body class="page-pricing">

<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<main>

  <section class="page-hero page-hero-sm">
    <div class="section-inner text-center">
      <div class="section-label">Pricing</div>
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">Simple, transparent plans</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">No hidden fees. No per-seat surprises. Cancel any time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pricing-full">
    <div class="section-inner">

      <div class="pricing-cards pricing-cards-lg">

        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="plan-header">
            <div class="plan-name">Starter</div>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price-amount">$49</span>
              <span class="price-period">/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="plan-desc">One campus. Up to 3 admins. Core key and door tracking.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features plan-features-full">
            <li class="feat-yes">1 campus building</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">3 admin users</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Physical key checkout &amp; recovery</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Door records &amp; fob profiles</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Staff &amp; safe management</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Audit log (30-day retention)</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Email overdue alerts</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">CSV import &amp; export</li>
            <li class="feat-no">Floor plan management</li>
            <li class="feat-no">Key agreement workflows</li>
            <li class="feat-no">Ring checkout system</li>
            <li class="feat-no">Priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-navy btn-full">Contact sales</a>
          <p class="plan-trial-note">14-day free trial &nbsp;·&nbsp; Setup within 24 hours</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Campus (featured) -->
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-featured">
          <div class="plan-badge">Most popular</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <div class="plan-name">Campus</div>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price-amount">$199</span>
              <span class="price-period">/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="plan-desc">Multi-building teams that need the full workflow. Starter plus every feature add-on and four extra buildings &mdash; bundled, never marked up.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features plan-features-full">
            <li class="feat-yes">Up to 5 campus buildings</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Unlimited admin users</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Physical key checkout &amp; recovery</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Door records &amp; fob profiles</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Staff &amp; safe management</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Audit log (1-year retention)</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Email overdue alerts</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">CSV import &amp; export</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Floor plan management</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Key agreement workflows</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Ring checkout system</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold btn-full">Contact sales</a>
          <p class="plan-trial-note">14-day free trial &nbsp;·&nbsp; Setup within 24 hours</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Enterprise -->
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="plan-header">
            <div class="plan-name">Enterprise</div>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price-amount">Custom</span>
            </div>
            <p class="plan-desc">Dedicated instance for large or multi-institution deployments.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features plan-features-full">
            <li class="feat-yes">Unlimited campus buildings</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Unlimited admin users</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Everything in Campus plan</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Dedicated deployment (your data only)</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Custom subdomain</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">SSO / SAML integration</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">7-year audit retention</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Uptime SLA</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Dedicated onboarding &amp; support</li>
            <li class="feat-yes">Custom integrations on request</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-navy btn-full">Contact sales</a>
          <p class="plan-trial-note">Tailored quote &nbsp;·&nbsp; Pilot period available</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="pricing-trust-row">
        <div class="pricing-trust-badge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          Dedicated instance — your data is never shared with other tenants
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-trust-badge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          Full audit log included on every plan
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-trust-badge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          Account live within 24 hours
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-trust-badge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          No per-key or per-door limits
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="pricing-demo-note">Want to explore the app before committing? <a href="https://demo.keydog.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try the live demo &rarr;</a></p>

      <!-- Add-ons -->
      <div class="addons-section">
        <h2 class="addons-title">Add-ons</h2>
        <p class="addons-intro">Start with Starter and switch on exactly what you need. Pay only for what you add &mdash; and the totals always line up.</p>

        <div class="addons-group">
          <div class="addons-group-header">
            <span class="addons-group-label">Feature Add-ons</span>
            <span class="addons-group-badge">Starter &rarr; Campus</span>
          </div>
          <p class="addons-group-desc">Unlock individual Campus capabilities on a Starter plan. Turn on all six and add four extra buildings, and you have rebuilt the full Campus plan &mdash; for the exact Campus price, never a cent more.</p>
          <div class="addons-grid">
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Floor Plan Management</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Upload plans, pin keys &amp; doors to visual locations</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$20 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Key Agreement Workflows</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Auto-generated PDF key agreements with signature capture</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$20 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Ring Checkout System</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Keyring-level checkout and return tracking</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$15 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Priority Support</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">SLA-backed response time and a dedicated support channel</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$30 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Unlimited Admin Users</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Remove Starter&rsquo;s 3-admin cap &mdash; unlimited named admins</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$15 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Extended Retention &mdash; 1 year</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Upgrade the 30-day audit log to a full year</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$10 <span class="addon-unit">/mo</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="addons-group-desc" style="margin-top:1.25rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">
            The math always closes: Starter <strong>$49</strong> + 4 extra buildings <strong>($40)</strong> + all six feature add-ons <strong>($110)</strong> = <strong>$199</strong> &mdash; identical to the Campus plan. Switch on any subset; you only ever pay for what you use, and you can never overpay by mixing and matching.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="addons-group">
          <div class="addons-group-header">
            <span class="addons-group-label">Capacity Add-ons</span>
            <span class="addons-group-badge">Any plan</span>
          </div>
          <p class="addons-group-desc">Need more room? These scale on top of Starter, Campus, or Enterprise &mdash; at the same flat per-unit rate on every plan, so growth is always predictable.</p>
          <div class="addons-grid">
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Extra Buildings</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Each campus building beyond your plan&rsquo;s included count &mdash; same rate whether it&rsquo;s your 2nd or your 20th</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$10 <span class="addon-unit">/building/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Extra Admin Seats</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Add named admin seats beyond Starter&rsquo;s 3. Campus and Enterprise already include unlimited admins</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$5 <span class="addon-unit">/seat/mo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="addon-card">
              <div class="addon-info">
                <div class="addon-name">Long-term Retention</div>
                <div class="addon-desc">Step audit-log retention up to 3 years ($25/mo) or 7 years ($40/mo). Campus includes 1 year; Enterprise includes 7</div>
              </div>
              <div class="addon-price">$25 <span class="addon-unit">/mo &middot; 3-yr</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="faq">
        <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does the free trial work?</h3>
            <p>Every plan starts with a 14-day free trial. Contact our team and your account will be set up within 24 hours — you'll receive login details by email. No payment details needed to get started.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What counts as a "campus building"?</h3>
            <p>Any physical building you manage keys and doors for — dorms, academic buildings, rec centres, etc. Each one counts as one campus building in your plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?</h3>
            <p>Yes, at any time. Contact us and we'll handle the change. Upgrades take effect immediately; downgrades apply at the end of your billing period.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Where is my data stored?</h3>
            <p>Your data is stored on our managed infrastructure in isolated, private databases. Enterprise customers get a fully dedicated environment — no shared resources. Your data never mingles with other tenants'.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is there a per-key or per-door limit?</h3>
            <p>No hard limits. Track as many keys and doors as your campus needs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do add-ons work?</h3>
            <p>Add-ons are billed monthly on top of your base plan. Feature add-ons unlock individual Campus capabilities on a Starter plan &mdash; switch on all six and add four extra buildings and you have matched the Campus plan exactly, for the same $199. Capacity add-ons (buildings, admin seats, retention) scale on top of any plan at a flat per-unit rate, so mixing and matching never costs more than the equivalent plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does cancellation work?</h3>
            <p>Cancel any time by contacting us. Your data export is available for 30 days after cancellation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
